<p>We are located at Lanzhou University, a beautiful city which passed through by Yellow River (see e.g. <a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%85%B0%E5%B7%9E%E5%B8%82">Wikipedia: Lanzhou City</a>). We exchange ideas and work with our neighbors from <a href="http://iie.lzu.edu.cn/lzupage/B20180912024139.html">Institute of Innovation Ecology</a>, as well as with the colleagues from University of Haifa, Havard University and etc.</p>

<p>实验室位于黄河穿城而过的美丽城市——兰州市。课题组和以色列海法大学，美国哈佛大学等科研单位有广泛的合作与交流。</p>

<p><strong>We are  looking for passionate new PhD students, Postdocs, Master students and undergraduate students to join the team</strong> <a href="http://localhost:4000/vacancies">(more info)</a> <strong>!</strong></p>

<p><strong>欢迎对进化生物学感兴趣的同学报考课题组的研究生，也欢迎来自兰州大学的本科生来实验室进行科研训练</strong></p>

<p>We are grateful for funding from Lanzhou University and <a href="http://www.nsfc.gov.cn/">National Natural Science Foundation of China (NSFC)</a>.</p>

